name: Desktop Test
description: As a user, I would like to select products from desktop

children.name: Verify that the products arrange in alphabetical order
children.description:
top menu tabdrop down option
DesktopsShow AllDesktops
Laptops & NotebooksShow AllLaptops & Notebooks

children.name: Verify that the products arrange in alphabetical order
Given User navigates to homepage
When User mouse hovers and clicks "Desktops" tab and clicks
And User select "Show AllDesktops"
And User selects sort by position "Name (Z - A)"
Then User can view products displayed in alphabetical order.
Verify that the products arrange in alphabetical order
Given User navigates to homepage
When User mouse hovers and clicks "Laptops & Notebooks" tab and clicks
And User select "Show AllLaptops & Notebooks"
And User selects sort by position "Name (Z - A)"
Then User can view products displayed in alphabetical order.

name: My Accounts
description: As a user, I would like to use all the options from My Account

children.name: Verify the user is able to login and logout successfully.
Given User navigates to homepage
When User clicks on My Account link
And User selects "Login" from the drop down
And User logs in with the following credentials
And User selects "Logout" from the drop down
Then User is able to view "Account Logout" heading
